channel.title: NONE of the servers I try work!
channel.description:
[glow=red,2,300][/glow]Okay, whenever I try to play, it says the server is down. This happens with the default (127.0.0.1), and all other servers I have tried. When I ping them, it says that the server has timed out. I have tried 10 different servers, and none of them have worked. If you know why, please help...
:confused: :confused: :confused:
BTW - I have Moparscape v3.2 Webclient, so don't tell me to download it.
